Title: check_livestatus
Component: core
State: open
Date: 2012-11-20 10:39:53
Targetversion: future
Class: feature

We could write a small check_livestatus in C (diet?) that
checks if Livestatus is working by just getting the versions
of Nagios, Check_MK and maybe the Nagios uptime. This could
then be used as a host check for the status_hosts and in a multisite
setup.
